  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >經典劇情向回合制rpg。</h2>經歷了亡國的悲劇，為了拯救青梅竹馬的公主，主角<strong>古拉迪奧</strong>在被囚禁之地<strong>斯拉夫城</strong>開啟一段拯救和自我救贖的冒險。<br>本作採用組隊冒險的模式，共有三位元主要女性角色可以加入隊伍（均可攻略）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632310/extras/2383b68f2b3defbe70ad171381122ea0.avif?t=1630712474\" width=400 height=550 /></span>伊莉雅（Ilia）王國的公主，古拉迪奧的青梅竹馬。戰敗被俘後在斯拉夫城做著娼婦的工作，再次遇見古拉迪奧的時候性格身心都發生了改變。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632310/extras/4ca15428f1fc3cf34d661e66f960282f.avif?t=1630712474\" width=400 height=550 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632310/extras/9bb2479e403c14d03ac6c9c7b6ed7773.avif?t=1630712474\" width=400 height=550 /></span>克勞迪婭（Cloudia）帝國的祭司，不折不扣的傲嬌少女，同時是個神棍。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632310/extras/1b8ad5854953fc0ce04d01b738713ea0.avif?t=1630712474\" width=400 height=550 /></span>普莉牧洛絲（Primrose）帝國的騎士，帶領軍隊攻破主角所在的城市，並親自將古拉迪奧等人俘虜。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>---------------------------------</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>提示：本作有輕微至中度的ntr傾向，過敏的玩家請酌情遊玩。</strong></h2>",
